column1: How familiar are you with the concept of artificial intelligence (A.I)?
column2: In your opinion, will A.I have a positive impact on our future?

column13: How concerned are you about the potential for A.I to be used for unethical or malicious purposes?
column14: In your opinion, could A.I potentially become a threat to humanity?
column15: How do you think A.I will impact the economy?
